      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe${sound:npc_Nophee_9825_qu_02.ogg}<BR>I was about to tell you about that anyway. It is not an easy task for ordinary people to manage magical devices.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-accepting-acceptted" mid="71" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Mana is a natural energy so it tends to change a lot like the weather. Mana can flow freely on some days and dry up on others.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2109_inventor_narlin-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2109_inventor_narlin-1-" mid="12" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Inventor Narlin$<BR>Haha, I don’t understand any of this!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-a" mid="14" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe${sound:npc_Nophee_9826_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Especially if there’s a powerful <FONT color=#a82424>Nest</FONT> created nearby, the <FONT color=#a82424>flow of mana tends to become unstable</FONT>. To preserve the <FONT color=#086171>relic’s barrier</FONT>, we need to measure the flow of mana all the time and manage its supply. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-b" mid="16" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe${sound:npc_Nophee_9826_qu_02.ogg}<BR>There is a <FONT color=#a82424>device</FONT> that I requested <FONT color=#086171>Narlin</FONT> to make. Using that, even an ordinary person can detect the flow of mana nearby and respond quickly.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-c" mid="18" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Since <FONT color=#086171>Narlin</FONT> is an excellent inventor, maybe he has finished making it by now. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2" mid="20" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Let me go and check!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-2" image="QN_NPC_Engineer_Hubert.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2-" mid="22" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Then in the meantime, I will ask Shalica to inform Vernicka about the device. Hmm... maybe I should make a simple instruction manual too. I should get to work now.<BR><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>* Talk to </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Inventor Narlin</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> at Rhadames.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2109_inventor_narlin-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2109_inventor_narlin-2-a" mid="24" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Inventor Narlin$<BR>Wow, I can’t help but be amazed every time I look at it. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Narlin is looking at a blueprint.)</FONT> Hmm? You look familiar... Where have I seen you before?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2109_inventor_narlin-2-a" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400619" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2109_inventor_narlin-2-b" mid="26" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Inventor Narlin$<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>? Hmm... Yes, maybe I saw you somewhere before... I’m just kidding! Haha. How can I forget a capable young fellow like you? Oh, you came for the device <FONT color=#086171>Norfe</FONT> requested? Of course it’s ready. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Narlin hands over a small device that can be held in one hand.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2109_inventor_narlin-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2109_inventor_narlin-3" mid="28" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Inventor Narlin$<BR>I followed the blueprint but it has such a complicated structure that I’m not sure I made it correctly. Lord <FONT color=#086171>Norfe </FONT> always comes up with extraordinary ideas. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2109_inventor_narlin-3" image="QN_Nophee.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2109_inventor_narlin-3-" mid="30" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Inventor Narlin$<BR>Are you leaving so soon? I’ll miss having your company. Come again when you’re free and we can have a little chat.<BR>
<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>* Go to </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Norfe</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> in Merca's Heart and show him the device.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-3-a" mid="32" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(His hat is sliding from his head and he seems to be out of breath.)</FONT> Oh... You’re... back...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-3-b" mid="34" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What’s going on?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-3-c" mid="36" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>I was away to do something and it took longer than I expected so I rushed back. I didn’t want to miss you when you were here, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. Is that the <FONT color=#a82424>device</FONT> I ordered?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-3-d" mid="38" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>Let me see… <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Norfe turns the device and studies it from every angle.)</FONT> Indeed. <FONT color=#086171>Narlin</FONT> is amazing. Other people would have taken days to complete this and he finished it within such a short period of time. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-3-e" mid="40" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe${sound:npc_Nophee_9826_qu_03.ogg}<BR>However, I can’t say that my blueprint is perfect. We need to test this <FONT color=#a82424>mana detector</FONT> first to make sure it’s working… And I need your help for that, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-3-e" image="QW_127.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
